channel.title: Chinese Democracy!
channel.description:
Ok, GNR isn't what it used to be. Of all former members, only AXL Rose remains. But still, we've waited for this album for 10 years so it should be good! I have the honor to download the final leak, and although I've only listened to Better, it's quite good. There are some great solo's, and AXL's voice is not bad either. However, it has a bit more of a techno influence. Just a tad bit though.
If you can't wait, you can check the pirate bay or another torrent site to download. I'm not sure if you can find it, but I GOT IT BIATCH!
